data.description: A Ranch home with a twist you must see to appreciate, with one floor living at its best including 3 bedrooms , primary bedroom bathroom, main full bath, living room, kitchen with dining area attached, laundry room and large back deck to enjoy your private backyard with hot tub is just the start! Now venture to your lower level that has the bonus of a 3 car garage, workshop plus additional living area that would make a perfect game room/movie room or just a large living room, cedar closet, and half bath that is attached to additional office/bedroom. The possibilities are endless and all with the convivence of being close to town with 1.94 acres of land! Come tour this unique property today before it's gone!!!
